🚀 Overview
A collection of Python-based mathematical models and algorithms designed for AI system optimization and high-fidelity data validation. This repository demonstrates technical reasoning applied to Large Language Models (LLMs) and Reinforcement Learning from Human Feedback (RLHF).
🛠 Key Features
Optimization Algorithms: Implementations of gradient-based optimization for model tuning.
Technical Reasoning Logic: Scripts for validating mathematical proofs and logical consistency in AI responses.
Data Quality Metrics: Tools for calculating accuracy and bias scores in large-scale annotation batches.
Bilingual Capability: Support for multi-language (English/Swahili) dataset processing.
💻 Tech Stack
Languages: Python (NumPy, SciPy)
Domains: Machine Learning, Linear Algebra, Calculus, UI/UX Analysis
Platforms: Integrated with workflows for Mercor, Aligner, and Handshake AI.
